{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0d1d55de70","title":"在重庆机场发表的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6a56a8d9dd","index":0,"year":1945,"month":8,"day":28,"articleId":"0d1d55de70","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"对话","id":"314ad57c4d","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenji4","name":"毛泽东文集第四卷（1999）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"中央文献研究室","files":"/books/wenji4.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenji4":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f37b1bef60","type":"title","text":"在重庆机场发表的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"0d1d55de70","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d124de2cc5","type":"paragraph","text":"本人此次来渝，系应国民政府主席蒋介石先生之邀请，商讨团结建国大计。现在抗日战争已经胜利结束，中国即将进入和平建设时期，当前时机极为重要。目前最迫切者，为保证国内和平，实施民主政治，巩固国内团结。国内政治上军事上所存在的各项迫切问题，应在和平、民主、团结的基础上加以合理解决，以期实现全国之统一，建设独立、自由与富强的新中国。希望中国一切抗日政党及爱国志士团结起来，为实现上述任务而共同奋斗。本人对于蒋介石先生之邀请，表示谢意。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"0d1d55de70","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"60ea566c07","type":"paragraph","text":"根据一九四五年八月二十九日","index":2,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"0d1d55de70","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"91111d5b24","type":"paragraph","text":"《新华日报》刊印。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"0d1d55de70","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":33,"end":33}}}},"__N_SSG":true}